OL,3,C'Easily led' father who threw rocks
OL,4,Cand bin at riot police jailed
OL,6,FAn "easily led" father-of-three who
OL,7,Fthrew rocks and a wheelie bin at riot
OL,8,Fpolice guarding a hotel housing asylum
OL,9,Fseekers has been jailed.
OL,11,FSonny Ackerman, 30, was sentenced to
OL,12,Ftwo years and four months for his part
OL,13,Fin the the violence outside the
OL,14,FHoliday Inn Express, in Rotherham, on
OL,15,F4 August.
OL,17,FJudge Jeremy Richardson KC told
OL,18,FAckerman he would have received an
OL,19,Feven longer sentence but for his clear
OL,20,Flearning disability.
