OL,3,C'Easily led' father who threw rocks
OL,4,Cand bin at riot police jailed
OL,6,FHe said: "I have little doubt you're
OL,7,Feasily led.
OL,9,F"I very much doubt you even understood
OL,10,Fwhat the disorder was all about."
OL,12,FBut Judge Richardson added: "You knew
OL,13,Fwhat you were doing and knew it was
OL,14,Fwrong."
OL,16,FSheffield Crown Court was shown
OL,17,Ffootage of a masked Ackerman throwing
OL,18,Fa rock at police lines at the height
OL,19,Fof the disorder.
