OL,6,FFurther video showed the defendant
OL,7,Fhelping to hurl a wheelie bin at the
OL,8,Fofficers who were trying to push back
OL,9,Fthe rioters.
OL,11,FThis happened close to a larger bin,
OL,12,Fwhich had been set alight against the
OL,13,Ffire door of the building.
OL,15,FJudge Richardson heard that Ackerman
OL,16,Fwas on bail for an offence of driving
OL,17,Fwhile disqualified at the time of the
OL,18,Frioting.
