OL,3,C'Easily led' father who threw rocks
OL,4,Cand bin at riot police jailed
OL,6,FThe judge said he had received a
OL,7,Freport from a neuropsychologist and
OL,8,Ftold the defendant it was clear he had
OL,9,Fa learning disability and a very low
OL,10,FIQ.
OL,12,FThe judge said: "This was a
OL,13,Fdisgraceful episode. It shocked the
OL,14,Fentire country.
OL,16,F"Those involved were an ignorant mob
OL,17,Fand they must be punished.
OL,19,F"You were part of that ignorant mob."
