OL,3,C'Easily led' father who threw rocks
OL,4,Cand bin at riot police jailed
OL,6,FAckerman, of Ashton-on-Ribble,
OL,7,FPreston, pleaded guilty to violent
OL,8,Fdisorder at a previous hearing and
OL,9,Fappeared in court on Tuesday via
OL,10,Fvideolink from prison.
OL,12,FHe is the latest of more than 70 men
OL,13,Fwho have been jailed after the rioting
OL,14,Fat the hotel.
OL,16,FThe court heard that the residents
OL,17,Fwere trapped on the upper floors of
OL,18,Fthe building as rioters broke in and
OL,19,Fstarted the fire in a bin at one of
OL,20,Fthe exits, filling the hotel with
OL,21,Fsmoke.
